{"sha": "a8b79cc939d6786293f654c42a2d1b0ab040de0e", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0MTM2NTMxMDA6YThiNzljYzkzOWQ2Nzg2MjkzZjY1NGM0MmEyZDFiMGFiMDQwZGUwZQ==", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Harald Anlauf", "email": "anlauf@gmx.de", "date": "2021-05-05T13:25:50Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Harald Anlauf", "email": "anlauf@gmx.de", "date": "2021-05-05T13:25:50Z"}, "message": "PR fortran/100274 - ICE in gfc_conv_procedure_call, at fortran/trans-expr.c:6131\n\nWhen the check for the length of formal and actual character arguments\nfound a mismatch and emitted a warning, it would skip further checks\nlike that could lead to errors.  Fix that by continuing the checking.\nAlso catch a NULL pointer dereference.\n\ngcc/fortran/ChangeLog:\n\n\tPR fortran/100274\n\t* interface.c (gfc_compare_actual_formal): Continue checks after\n\temitting warning for argument length mismatch.\n\t* trans-expr.c (gfc_conv_procedure_call): Check for NULL pointer\n\tdereference.\n\ngcc/testsuite/ChangeLog:\n\n\tPR fortran/100274\n\t* gfortran.dg/argument_checking_25.f90: New test.", "tree": {"sha": "03f0d8b2532c9e139e588d1fdd1ab1c8fe494560", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/trees/03f0d8b2532c9e139e588d1fdd1ab1c8fe494560"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/commits/a8b79cc939d6786293f654c42a2d1b0ab040de0e", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/a8b79cc939d6786293f654c42a2d1b0ab040de0e", "html_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commit/a8b79cc939d6786293f654c42a2d1b0ab040de0e", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/a8b79cc939d6786293f654c42a2d1b0ab040de0e/comments", "author": {"login": "harald-anlauf", "id": 90786862, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjkwNzg2ODYy", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/90786862?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/harald-anlauf", "htm